,{"pid":"7b977350147139582c1192517978a1dfe6cfaf4d","tid":2129023,"uid":59511,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T10:24:40.000Z","msg":"刁總：係我飛你先架<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1342ae9856d81521420c91add82faa1fb1acdab7","tid":2129023,"uid":279938,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T10:28:39.000Z","msg":"真.逃犯天堂"},{"pid":"8b9d7a77eb29d9fb2e442fc59e3a68e09466b46c","tid":2129023,"uid":173002,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T10:29:03.000Z","msg":"香港係暴政、強國係一黨專政，搵歐美民主選舉國家比，顯得香港暴政更獨裁陰險。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"677dae140d7a746674e08a35192348e1e964b86b","tid":2129023,"uid":279938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T10:31:05.000Z","msg":"有冇人知道港共有冇取消同美國簽訂嘅刑事司法互助協議？"},{"pid":"c6b54d65dbd98e858029c132ebe89d498062f1c5","tid":2129023,"uid":173002,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1342ae9856d81521420c91add82faa1fb1acdab7","tid":2129023,"uid":279938,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T10:28:39.000Z","msg":"真.逃犯天堂"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T10:32:12.000Z","msg":"香港政權：陳同佳自己飛去台灣自首，唔洗<br />\n使同台灣傾移交。<br />\n英加澳紐：既然香港暴政認為逃犯會自己自首，唔使同香港維持引渡協議。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58a7c2074f6382e5b8533df5aafd1ce0421b6c4d","tid":2129023,"uid":18258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T10:33:51.000Z","msg":"喜迎加速<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}